siasat alkhususia
----------------
### almuqadima
satusaeiduk siasat alkhususiat alkhasat bina ealaa fahm almaelumat alati najmaeuha fi Safa Azkar, wakayf tastakhdimuha Safa Azkar, walkhiarat almutahat lika.
samamat Safa Azkar tatbiq Safa Azkar katatbiq majaani. yatimu tawfir hadhih alkhidmat biwasitat Safa Azkar mjanan wahi mukhasasat lilaistikhdam kama hi.
'iidha aikhtart aistikhdam khidmatina, fa'iinak tuafuq ealaa jame almaelumat waistikhdamiha fima yataealaq bihadhih alsiyasati. tustkhdm almaelumat alshakhsiat alati najmaeuha litawfir alkhidmat watahsiniha. lan nastakhdim maelumatik 'aw nusharikuha mae 'ayi shakhs biaistithna' ma hu muadih fi siasat alkhususiat hadhihi.
almustalahat almustakhdamat fi siasat alkhususiat hadhih laha nafs almaeani alwaridat fi alshurut wal'ahkam alkhasat bina, walati yumkin alwusul 'iilayha ealaa mawqieina al'iiliktruni, ma lam yatima taerifuha bikhilaf dhalik fi siasat alkhususiat hadhihi.
### jame almaelumat waistikhdamiha
lilhusul ealaa tajribat 'afdal 'athna' aistikhdam khidmatina, qad natlub mink tazwidana bimaelumat taerif shakhsiat mueayanatin, bima fi dhalik ealaa sabil almithal la alhasr aism almustakhdam waeunwan albarid al'iiliktrunii waljins walmawqie walsuwari. sayatimu alaihtifaz bialmaelumat alati natlubuha min qiblina waistikhdamuha kama hu muadih fi siasat alkhususiat hadhihi.
yastakhdim altatbiq khidamat altaraf althaalith alati qad tajmae maelumat tustakhdam litahdid huiatiki.
## milafaat taerif aliartibat
milafaat taerif alairtibat hi milafaat tahtawi ealaa kamiyat saghirat min albayanat tustkhdm eadtan kamaerif farid majhul alhuiati. yatimu 'iirsaluha 'iilaa mutasafihik min mawqie alwib aladhi tazuruh wayatimu takhzinuha ealaa aldhaakirat aldaakhiliat li'ajhizatika.
la tastakhdim hadhih alkhadamat "milafaat taerif alairtibati" hadhih srahtan. wamae dhalika, qad yastakhdim altatbiq 'akwad wamaktabat tabieatan lijihat kharijiat tastakhdim "milafat taerif alairtibatu" lijame almaelumat watahsin khadamatiha. ladayk khiar qabul 'aw rafd milafaat taerif alairtibat hadhihi, wamaerifat mataa yatimu 'iirsal milafi taerif airtibat 'iilaa jihazika. 'iidha aikhtart rafd milafaat taerif alairtibat alkhasat bina, faqad la tatamakan min aistikhdam baed 'ajza' hadhih alkhidmati.
### maelumat almawqie
qad tastakhdim baed alkhadamat maelumat almawqie almanqulat min alhawatif almahmulat lilmustakhdimina. nastakhdim hadhih almaelumat faqat fi alnitaq aldarurii lilkhidmat almuhadadati.
### maelumat aljihaz
najmae maelumat min jihazik fi baed alhalati. sayatimu aistikhdam almaelumat litawfir khidmat 'afdal wamane al'aemal alaihtialiati. bial'iidafat 'iilaa dhalika, lan tatadaman hadhih almaelumat almaelumat alati tuhadid huiat almustakhdim alfardi.
### muqadimu alkhidma
qad nuazif sharikat wafradan min jihat kharijiat lil'asbab altaaliati:
* litashil khidmatina;
* litaqdim alkhidmat niabat euna;
* li'ada' khidmat mutaealiqat bialkhidmati; 'aw
* limusaeadatina fi tahlil kayfiat astikhdam khidmatina.
nurid 'an nabligh mustakhdimi hadhih alkhidmat 'ana hadhih aljihat alkharijiat ladayha haqu alwusul 'iilaa maelumatik alshakhsiati. walsabab hu 'ada' almahami almuakalat 'iilayhim niabat eunaa. wamae dhalika, fahum mulzamun bieadam alkashf ean almaelumat 'aw aistikhdamiha li'ayi gharad akhar.
### al'aman
nahn nuqadir thiqatak fi tazwidina bimaelumatik alshakhsiati, wabialtaali naseaa jahidin liaistikhdam wasayil maqbulat tjaryan lihimayitiha. walakin tadhkar 'anah la tujad tariqat naql eabr al'iintirnit 'aw tariqat takhzin 'iiliktruniin aminat wamawthuqat binisbat 100%, wala yumkinuna daman 'amaniha almutlaqi.
### khususiat al'atfal
la tastahdif hadhih alkhadamat 'aya shakhs yaqilu eumruh ean 13 eaman. wala najmae ean qasd maelumat taerif shakhsiat min al'atfal aladhin tuqilu 'aemaruhum ean 13 eaman. wafi halat aiktishafina 'ana tflan yaqilu eumruh ean 13 eaman qad zawadana bimaelumat shakhsiatin, fa'iinana nahdhifuha ealaa alfawr min khawadimna. 'iidha kunt 'ahad alwalidayn 'aw alwasi wakunt ealaa eilm bi'ana tiflak qad zawadana bimaelumat shakhsiatin, fayurjaa alaitisal bina hataa natamakan min aitikhadh al'iijra'at allaazimati.
### altaghyirat ealaa siasat alkhususiat hadhih
qad naqum bitahdith siasat alkhususiat alkhasat bina min waqt lakhir. wabialtaali, nansahuk bimurajaeat hadhih alsafhat bishakl dawriin limaerifat 'ayi taghyirati. wasanaqum bi'iikhtarik bi'ayi taghyirat min khilal nashr siasat alkhususiat aljadidat ealaa hadhih alsafhati. tusri hadhih altaghyirat fwran baed nashriha ealaa hadhih alsafhati.
### atasal bina
'iidha kanat ladayk 'ayu 'asyilat 'aw aiqtirahat hawl siasat alkhususiat alkhasat bina, fala tataradad fi alaitisal bina.
maelumat alaitisali:
albarid al'iilikturuni: eng.taher.shaker@gmail.com
